i\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個同民主背道而馳嘅人走出黎同你講要爭取民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋之後梁天琦自己都confirm左，佢話呢種集體主義，係無可避免嘅，有時要取捨，我唔明點解無人留意到，定還是你班獨派係fascist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係港大唔知呢d野<br />\n平心而論, 梁天琦畀輿論遺棄, 主要係立法會選舉同熱普城爭拗+宣誓案後失蹤, 好似未必關你講個d性格 / 風格問題事<br />\n我記得你個post, 係因為個陣成個高登真係當佢神咁拜, 你應該係第一個夠膽開post批評佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一早睇穿條友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過anyway<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8003b3a98fb0d8f2f806ad5e790c2298b36aeb11","tid":187002,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:33:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講多兩嘴又問你dse幾分 係咪葡萄佢做天之驕子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾行為點都係垃圾, 理撚得你係愛因斯坦夾埋巴菲特捉住條毒撚向佢下體滴蠟都係垃圾行為黎架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f2d475f8ac5dc78a69d73015f0e0bcbeeddbba","tid":187002,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:36:59.000Z","msg":"其實港大hall有咁大問題係咪因為入住權係宿生會到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇方法收返去大學到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6762814c2644d1552fe817ad82c30d3232e6627","tid":187002,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實港大hall有咁大問題係咪因為入住權係宿生會到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇方法收返去大學到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWarden唔會理"},{"pid":"d412b3a41bfa511270209cf43b77a6192b1bd9cc","tid":187002,"uid":81075,"like":0,"dislike